Why opensource your secrets
-------------------------------
1. improves your design
You have to improve it, because your code 
- must be modular
- must be documented
- clean up your interfaces

2. Great for PR & recruitment
- devs can 
- you don't get poor-fit developers for your company

3. Improves your product
- great ideas for free

Caveats
- don't open source the whole platform, pick showcases carefully
- the open source part must be small enough so you don't spend 2 years redesigning

